## 10. Detailed Data Flow

### Master Flow — Query Lifecycle

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User types NL query in chat<br/>within Electron blotter] --> B{Classify intent}
    
    B -->|"🔍 New Search<br/>e.g., 'Show FX trades > $1M'"| C[Frontend sends NL query<br/>to Backend LLM Proxy]
    B -->|"⚙️ Grid Manipulation<br/>e.g., 'Sort by date desc'"| D[AG Grid AI Toolkit path]
    B -->|"💬 Non-search<br/>e.g., 'What can you do?'"| E[Handle as chat-only<br/>response — no query generated]
    
    %% New Search Path
    C --> F[LLM Proxy validates TEA token]
    F -->|Invalid| F1[Return 401 — show<br/>re-auth prompt in chat]
    F -->|Valid| G[Proxy builds prompt:<br/>system prompt + trade schema<br/>+ NL query + conversation context]
    G --> H[Call AWS Bedrock<br/>Claude 3.5 Sonnet]
    
    H --> I[Bedrock returns<br/>structured query JSON]
    I --> J{Proxy validates response}
    
    J -->|"❌ Invalid JSON"| K[Retry once with<br/>stricter prompt + error context]
    K --> H
    
    J -->|"❌ Retry also failed"| L[Return error to frontend<br/>'Could not understand.<br/>Try rephrasing.']
    
    J -->|"⚠️ Clarification needed"| M[Return clarification question<br/>to frontend]
    M --> M1[Show question in chat bubble<br/>e.g., 'Did you mean FX Spot or FX Swap?']
    M1 --> A
    
    J -->|"✅ Valid"| N[Proxy logs: user ID, query,<br/>generated JSON, model, latency]
    N --> O[Return validated query JSON<br/>+ display message to frontend]
    
    O --> P[Frontend extracts<br/>filter chips from JSON]
    P --> Q[Frontend sends query<br/>via WebSocket + TEA token]
    Q --> R[Trade server executes query<br/>and returns results]
    R --> S[AG Grid SSRM populates<br/>with trade data]
    S --> T[Chat shows:<br/>'Found N trades matching<br/>your criteria']
    
    %% Grid Manipulation Path
    D --> D1["gridApi.getStructuredSchema()"]
    D1 --> D2[Send schema + NL command<br/>to Bedrock via proxy]
    D2 --> D3[Bedrock returns<br/>new grid state JSON]
    D3 --> D4["gridApi.setState(newState)"]
    D4 --> D5[SSRM re-fetches<br/>with new filters/sort]
    D5 --> S
```

